  • Incident Date: 2025-04-04
  • City: OMAHA
  • State: NE
  • Report Type: Undeclared Shipment with no Release
  • Mode Of Transportation: Air
  • Carrier/Reporter: UNITED PARCEL SERVICE CO.
  • Hazmat Fatalities: 0
  • Hazmat Injuries: 0
  • Non-Hazmat Fatalities: 0
  • Total Amount Of Damages: 0
  • Serious Incident Ind: No
  • Description: ONE AIR PACKAGE WAS INSPECTED DUE TO VISIBLE TRIGGERS OF POSSIBLE DANGEROUS GOODS SHOWN ON THE OUTER BOX. THE OUTER BOX HAS A PICTURE OF A VACUUM, PHOTO OF A BATTERY PACK, AND ONE END HAS A TINY LI-ION IMPRINTED ON THE BOX. UPON INSPECTION OF THE CONTENTS DISCOVERED ONE LITHIUM ION BATTERY, 57 WATT HOURS THAT IS PACKED SEPARATE FROM THE VACUUM. OUTER BOX DOES NOT HAVE A BATTERY MARK APPLIED. THE PACKAGE WAS SHIPPED FROM NEBRASKA USING UPS ACCOUNT X320F4, AMAZON.COM.KYDC, INC #OMA2, 14248 HIGHWAY 370, OMAHA NE 68138.
